    "The development,  by reason of the cumulative depth of extensions, as well as the poor quality appearance of the structure. appears as a dominant and visually intrusive form of development, which also results in a cramped over-development of the site, out of scale and character with neighbouring development, to the detriment of future occupiers and the character of the surrounding area contrary to Policy 7 of the Havering Local Plan.",
